    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-02-06T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-02-06T00:00:00-05:00" n="358"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d358">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">Hopkins Papers</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The President’s Special Assistant</hi> (<persName
                        corresp="#p_HHL1" type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Hopkins</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">President</gloss>
                    </hi>
                    <note n="1" xml:id="d358fn1">This note is undated, but the content indicates
                        that it was passed to the President during <persName corresp="#p_S16"
                            >Stalin</persName>’s extended statement on the Polish question during
                        the Third Plenary Meeting on February 6, 1945. See <hi rend="italic"
                            >ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_670">p. 670</ref>.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Yalta</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-02-06">February 6,
                            1945.</date>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Mr. President</hi>
                </p>
                <p>Why not let this wind up today when <persName corresp="#p_S16">Stalin</persName>
                    is thru—and say we will talk it over again tomorrow. It is 7.15</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_HHL1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Harry</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
